AWS Glue Sales ETL — Important Commands Cheat Sheet
🔹 AWS Configure
aws configure

🪣 S3 Commands
List all buckets
aws s3 ls
List bucket files
aws s3 ls s3://BUCKET_NAME --recursive
Upload file
aws s3 cp sales_2024_q1.csv s3://BUCKET_NAME/
Delete all bucket contents + bucket
aws s3 rb s3://BUCKET_NAME --force
Check object versions
aws s3api list-object-versions --bucket BUCKET_NAME
Delete specific object version
aws s3api delete-object `  --bucket BUCKET_NAME `  --key "FILE_PATH" `  --version-id VERSION_ID

🔹 Glue Commands
List Glue jobs
aws glue list-jobs
List crawlers
aws glue list-crawlers
List databases
aws glue get-databases
Get tables
aws glue get-tables --database-name sales_db
Get job runs
aws glue get-job-runs `  --job-name sales_etl_job `  --region us-east-1
Delete Glue job
aws glue delete-job --job-name sales_etl_job
Delete crawler
aws glue delete-crawler --name sales_raw_crawler
Delete database
aws glue delete-database --name sales_db

📊 Athena Commands
Start Athena query
aws athena start-query-execution `  --query-string "SELECT * FROM sales LIMIT 10;" `  --query-execution-context Database=sales_db `  --result-configuration OutputLocation=s3://ATHENA_BUCKET/results/ `  --region us-east-1
Get Athena query results
aws athena get-query-results `  --query-execution-id QUERY_ID `  --region us-east-1 `  --query "ResultSet.Rows[*].Data[*].VarCharValue" `  --output text
List Athena workgroups
aws athena list-work-groups
Delete Athena workgroup
aws athena delete-work-group `  --work-group WORKGROUP_NAME `  --recursive-delete-option

📜 CloudWatch Logs
List log groups
aws logs describe-log-groups
Show only log group names
aws logs describe-log-groups `  --query "logGroups[].logGroupName" `  --output text
Delete log group
aws logs delete-log-group `  --log-group-name "/aws-glue/jobs/error"

🔐 IAM Commands
List IAM roles
aws iam list-roles
Delete IAM role
aws iam delete-role --role-name ROLE_NAME
Detach policy from role
aws iam detach-role-policy `  --role-name ROLE_NAME `  --policy-arn POLICY_ARN

🧹 Cleanup Verification
Verify S3 is empty
aws s3 ls
Verify Glue clean
aws glue list-jobsaws glue list-crawlersaws glue get-databases
Verify CloudWatch clean
aws logs describe-log-groups
Verify Athena clean
aws athena list-work-groups
